<slide title="Basics - REST">
<break lines="1"/>
<blurb fontsize="4em">REST HTTP Methods</blurb>
<list>
<item>GET - Fetch resource(s) from WePay</item>
<item>POST - Create a new resource</item>
<item>PUT - Modify a resource</item>
<item>DELETE - Delete a resource</item>
</list>
<break lines="1"/>

<blurb fontsize="4em">HTTP Response Codes</blurb>
<list>
<item>200 - GET/PUT/DELETE request succeeded</item>
<item>201 - POST request succeeded (resource created)</item>
<item>400 - Parameter missing</item>
<item>403 - Forbidden</item>
<item>404 - Unknown API Call</item>
<item>405 - Method not allowed</item>
<item>500 - Internal Error - contact api@wepay.com</item>
</list>

</slide>
